OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy over
OL,6,Fthe Western Isles, and later northwest
OL,7,Fmainland, with rain, which may be
OL,8,Fheavy at times overnight. Elsewhere
OL,9,Fwill be dry and mostly cloudy but some
OL,10,Fclear spells. Strong winds easing in
OL,11,Fwest. Slight frost possible in the
OL,12,Feast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FPatchy rain slowly spreading
OL,15,Feast through the day although very
OL,16,Flittle in the east. Becoming dry and
OL,17,Fbrighter in the northwest through the
OL,18,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
